description: This skill allows Alexa to tell you interesting facts about United States national parks.  Ask Alexa to tell you a fact about national parks, and she will respond with a randomized park fact.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask national park facts to give me a national park fact
Alexa, ask national park facts to tell me something about national parks
Alexa, ask national park facts to tell me about national parks
name: National Park Facts
shortDescription: Learn fun facts about the United States National Parks!  Ask Alexa for a National Park Fact, and have her respond with an interesting park tidbit.
